commit.title: Add SPHINXWARNINGS variable that, when set, omits the Sphinx
commit.message:
Add SPHINXWARNINGS variable that, when set, omits the Sphinx
"treat errors as warnings" flag (-W).  This is a better setting
if you're editing documentation; otherwise you only get a
single warning for each "make sphinx".
